### ============================================
### MS-PROJECTS API - Green Yield Forge
### Porta: 8081
### ============================================

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8081/healthz

### Swagger Documentation
GET http://localhost:8081/api-docs

### ============================================
### PROJECTS API
### ============================================

### List all projects (paginated)
GET http://localhost:8081/projects?page=1&pageSize=10

### Search projects by name
GET http://localhost:8081/projects?search=aurora

### Create a new project
POST http://localhost:8081/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Fazenda Aurora",
  "location": "PR",
  "hectares": 200,
  "description": "Projeto de reflorestamento na Mata Atl√¢ntica",
  "certifier": "Verra"
}

### Get a project by ID (SUBSTITUA <id>)
GET http://localhost:8081/projects/<id>

### Update a project (SUBSTITUA <id>)
PUT http://localhost:8081/projects/<id>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Fazenda Aurora Updated",
  "location": "SC",
  "hectares": 250,
  "certifier": "Gold Standard"
}

### Delete a project (SUBSTITUA <id>)
DELETE http://localhost:8081/projects/<id>

### ============================================
### BATCHES API
### ============================================

### List all batches (paginated)
GET http://localhost:8081/batches?page=1&pageSize=10

### List batches by projectId (SUBSTITUA <projectId>)
GET http://localhost:8081/batches?projectId=<projectId>

### List batches by status
GET http://localhost:8081/batches?status=AVAILABLE

### Create a batch (SUBSTITUA <projectId>)
POST http://localhost:8081/batches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectId": "<projectId>",
  "tonsCO2": 40,
  "pricePerTon": 15,
  "status": "AVAILABLE"
}

### Get a batch by ID (SUBSTITUA <id>)
GET http://localhost:8081/batches/<id>

### Update a batch (SUBSTITUA <id>)
PUT http://localhost:8081/batches/<id>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectId": "<projectId>",
  "tonsCO2": 50,
  "pricePerTon": 18,
  "status": "SOLD"
}

### Partial update a batch
PUT http://localhost:8081/batches/<id>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "RESERVED"
}

### Delete a batch (SUBSTITUA <id>)
DELETE http://localhost:8081/batches/<id>

